Greetings from the Diplomacy* Adjudicator!!                   March 11, 1993
convoys

There are several vaariations on convoys that can be changed from their
non-strict default settings.

These allow players to be restricted to specifying only valid convoy orders
(thus removing, at least partially, the ability to communicate via invalid
orders in no-press games) and to switch to the original board-game definition
of the convoy order.

